<%= header_section("We couldn't verify your bank account yet.") %>
<div>
  <p>Hi there. You recently added a bank account for Gumroad payouts, and we weren't able to verify it yet. This can happen if the account or routing details have a typo — or simply because a newly opened account, or a recently added bank or branch, isn't in our payment partner's records yet.</p>
  <p>First, double-check your details in <%= link_to "your payout settings", settings_payments_url %>. If you're confident everything is correct, you don't need to do anything: new accounts and banks usually appear within a few days to a few weeks, and we'll automatically re-check yours once a week for up to <%= RetryStripeRejectedPayoutSetupsJob::RETRY_WINDOW_WEEKS %> weeks. We'll only email you again if we still can't verify it.</p>
</div>
